Package: pcdp-lint
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Post-Coding Development Paradigm specification linter
 pcdp-lint is a command-line tool for validating specification files written
 in the Post-Coding Development Paradigm format. It checks structural rules,
 validates metadata fields, and ensures compliance with deployment templates.
 .
 The tool supports linting individual specification files and can list all
 known deployment templates with their default target languages.